{"tha-ap464:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap464:0.2":"Salakusumiyavagga ","tha-ap464:0.3":"Citakapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap464:1.1":"“Jhayamanassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap464:1.2":"sikhino lokabandhuno; ","tha-ap464:1.3":"Attha campakapupphani, ","tha-ap464:1.4":"citakam abhiropayim. ","tha-ap464:2.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap464:2.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap464:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap464:2.4":"citapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap464:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap464:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap464:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap464:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap464:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap464:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap464:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap464:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap464:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap464:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma citakapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap464:7.1":"Citakapujakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}